api_list.description:
Extract SEO from any website.

Data extracted:

- Site **title**.
- Site **description**.
- Site **keywords**.
- **OG meta** tags.
- All site **headings**(H1, H2, H3, H4, H5, H6).
- And all **links**. *-- Coming soon.*
